{"tid":362664,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"到依家都仲係覺得保特好可惜","createTime":"2017-08-17T05:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T07:59:42.000Z","uid":2719,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a9c2ae7b6c579cbb5df7c81e9586dfc6896c5d","tid":362664,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:59:46.000Z","msg":"08年輕輕鬆鬆勁串咁破世界紀錄<br />\n之後比賽都keep住唔壓線<br />\n(其實我覺得已經有點自負 不可一世既感覺)<br />\n<br />\n依家退休戰想盡力跑都做唔到柒住傷<br />\n<br />\n到日後有人破佢紀錄<br />\n佢可能心諗屌我當年盡全力快過你啦<br />\n但都只係鳩up 現實係睇官方紀錄<br />\n<br />\n更可笑既可能仲會有啲小學雞唔識佢<br />\n仲串返佢轉頭話屌你收皮啦廢佬<br />\n<br />\n果刻<br />\n你估佢會唔會後悔 點解當年唔盡全力壓線..."},{"pid":"de38f14bf2919add0fc306cd046ecf098dfbfdee","tid":362664,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:23:34.000Z","msg":"唔會有人快過佢了"},{"pid":"fdfa157bf245b791d866248f142b1b791f3ec364","tid":362664,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會有人快過佢了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每次有人破紀錄<br />\n都會有人話應該無人破到<br />\n但將來實有人保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39328fd54dec86ee478ae2fea988cf406e536549","tid":362664,"uid":30773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會有人快過佢了</blockquote><br />\n二十年後d訓練技術會去到幾勁？<br />\n9秒4好似先係極限"},{"pid":"ca6869ea23d13238987340b95f8fbbda38826e62","tid":362664,"uid":54025,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"我尋日去跑 搵個fd幫我計，100米8秒47<br />\n<br />\n根本保特吹大左，我都快過佢"},{"pid":"cf23b6a8bcd5bc6482a33fee125fb912f9035e57","tid":362664,"uid":34852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我尋日去跑 搵個fd幫我計，100米8秒47<br />\n<br />\n根本保特吹大左，我都快過佢</blockquote><br />\n......"},{"pid":"74971afb28beb238d6b7d1aa0ff95f201a3330e1","tid":362664,"uid":12449,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:38:1